## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="83642-307">返回的对象的基础类型<xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlDocument.InvokeScript%2A>而异。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="83642-307">The underlying type of the object returned by <xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlDocument.InvokeScript%2A> will vary.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="83642-308">如果被调用的活动脚本函数返回标量数据，如字符串或整数，它将作为字符串返回。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="83642-308">If the called Active Scripting function returns scalar data, such as a string or an integer, it will be returned as a string.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="83642-309">如果它返回基于脚本的对象，如使用 JScript 或 VBScript 的创建对象`new`运算符的类型将为`Object`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="83642-309">If it returns a script-based object, such as an object created using JScript or VBScript's `new` operator, it will be of type `Object`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="83642-310">(您可以通过调用进行此类对象上调用<xref:System.Object.GetType%2A>并使用<xref:System.Type.InvokeMember%2A>。)如果它返回一个 HTML DOM 元素，如`DIV`或`TABLE`，它的类型将为`Object`; 如果已添加对 MSHTML 的项目引用。DLL，但是，它将转换为特定的非托管 DOM 类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="83642-310">(You can make calls on such objects by calling <xref:System.Object.GetType%2A> and using <xref:System.Type.InvokeMember%2A>.) If it returns an HTML DOM element, such as a `DIV` or a `TABLE`, it will be of type `Object`; if you have added a project reference to MSHTML.DLL, however, it will be cast to its specific unmanaged DOM type.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="83642-311">可以调用包括 JScript 和 VBScript 的用户的计算机上安装任何活动脚本语言编写的任何函数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="83642-311">You may call any function written in any Active Scripting language installed on the user's computer, including JScript and VBScript.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="83642-312"><xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlDocument.InvokeScript%2A> Nothing 如果用户已显式关闭 Internet Explorer 中执行脚本或网页上的当前安全配置不允许将执行操作。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="83642-312">The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.HtmlDocument.InvokeScript%2A> will do nothing if the user has explicitly turned off script execution in Internet Explorer, or if the current security configuration for the Web page does not allow it.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="83642-313">下面的代码示例在网页中执行脚本的内容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="83642-313">The following code example executes the contents of a script in a Web page.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="83642-314">代码示例，则需要<xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser>调用在应用程序中`WebBrowser1`，并且已加载以下 Web 页面。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="83642-314">The code example requires that you have a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser> in your application called `WebBrowser1`, and that you have loaded the following Web page.</span></span>  
  
```  
<HTML>  
  
    <HEAD>  
        <TITLE>Invoke Script Sample</TITLE>  
  
        <SCRIPT>  
            function MyObject() {  
                this.Data = "Data for my private object.";  
            }  
            // Return a string.  
            function test() {  
                return("This is a test.");  
            }  
            // Return a JScript object.  
            function testJScriptObject() {  
                return(new(MyObject));  
            }  
            // Return a DOM element.  
            function testElement() {  
                return(div1);  
            }  
        </SCRIPT>  
    </HEAD>  
  
    <BODY>  
  
        <DIV id="div1">  
        </DIV>  
  
    </BODY>  
  
</HTML>  
  
```  
  
